OL,4,G2300FCountdown to War
OL,5,     GOn 3rd September 1939, Britain
OL,6,     Gdeclared war. After a tense
OL,7,     Gultimatum and false alarm,
OL,8,     GBritish planes saw their first
OL,9,     Gaction and the SS Athenia was
OL,10,     Gtorpedoed, marking the first
OL,11,     Gcasualties.
